book.synopsis: It is a dark time for the New Republic. The Yuukhan Vong, despite some recent losses, continue to advance into the Core, and continue their relentless hunt for the Jedi. Now, in a desperate act of courage, Anakin Solo leads a Jedi strike force into the heart of Yuukhan Vong territory, where he hopes to destroy a major Vong anti-jedi weapon. There, with his brother and sister at his side, he will come fact to face with his destiny - as the New Republic, still fighting the good fight, will come face to face with theirs...
